author_ssm: Lauren Kata, with assistance from Kainaath Ahmad Shah Mumtaz, Ian Bryce Hoyt, and Arnav Vinay Kochar, 2019-2021.
unittitle_ssm: NYU Abu Dhabi Institute: Promotional and Program Materials
abstract_ssm: The collection "Records of the NYU Abu Dhabi Institute: Public Program Materials" documents over ten years' worth of events that took place at the Institute from 2007 through 2020, with the majority of the contents covering the years 2008 through 2015. This body of material from the Institute's first decade is relevant to anyone researching the early years of NYU Abu Dhabi as a way to understand the University's regional and global role in advancing research and scholarship, and exchanging knowledge collaboratively with the wider public.
